<div class="columns-row-custom">
<div class="one-third-custom">
<a href="http://shastabe.membeesites.net/trade-school-training/seminars-certifications/calendar/#cid=990&amp;wid=801"><span style="color: #0000ff;">CPR, AED, and First Aid For Adults:</span></a>

This Standard first Aid Course is designed to provide skills in first aid and accident prevention.  Students will learn Adult CPR, rescue breathing and choke saving, how to treat severe bleeding, fractures, bee stings, burns, etc.  Cal/OSHA requires a CPR/First Aid trained and certified employee on all job sites.
</div>

<div class="one-third-custom">
<a href="http://shastabe.membeesites.net/trade-school-training/seminars-certifications/calendar/#cid=990&amp;wid=801"><span style="color: #0000ff;">Forklift Operator:</span></a>

All employees who operate forklifts must be trained &amp; certified!!!  This class will present the "5 W's(Who,What,When, Why, and Where) of Forklift Operation and Certification."

This includes:
<ul>
 	<li>Instruction on forklift fatalities and injuries</li>
 	<li>Forklift stability and center of gravity</li>
 	<li>Operating rules</li>
 	<li>Load handling</li>
 	<li>Training and certification regulations</li>
 	<li>Pre-shift inspections</li>
 	<li>Hands on instruction</li>
 	<li>On-site evaluations</li>
</ul>
</div>


<div class="one-third-custom">
<a href="http://shastabe.membeesites.net/trade-school-training/seminars-certifications/calendar/#cid=990&amp;wid=801"><span style="color: #0000ff;">Flagging:</span></a>
<ul>
 	<li>Characteristics of a Flagger</li>
 	<li>Flagger clothing and equipment</li>
 	<li>Work zone layout and Flagger Station</li>
 	<li>Hand signaling procedures</li>
 	<li>One-lane, two-way traffic control</li>
 	<li>Typical lane closure</li>
 	<li>Flagging methods &amp; Flagger operation</li>
 	<li>Emergency situations and hostile drivers</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

